name: r-radiant.data
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.4.4" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-radiant.data
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/radiant.data_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/radiant.data/radiant.data_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 97444131f1d0a74255a72d9abec46c84246a7eb9c9763973d27e9ef7d3ff48d2

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dt >=0.9
    - r-mass
    - r-base64enc
    - r-broom >=0.5.2
    - r-bslib >=0.3.1
    - r-car >=3.0_0
    - r-curl >=2.5
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.7
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2.1
    - r-glue >=1.3.0
    - r-import >=1.1.0
    - r-jsonlite >=1.0
    - r-knitr >=1.20
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.4
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-markdown >=1.0
    - r-patchwork >=1.0.0
    - r-plotly >=4.7.1
    - r-png
    - r-psych >=1.8.4
    - r-randomizr >=0.20.0
    - r-readr >=1.1.1
    - r-readxl >=1.0.0
    - r-rlang >=0.4.10
    - r-rmarkdown >=1.14
    - r-rstudioapi >=0.7
    - r-scales >=0.4.0
    - r-shiny >=1.7.1
    - r-shinyace >=0.4.1
    - r-shinyfiles >=0.9.1
    - r-stringi >=1.2.4
    - r-tibble >=1.4.2
    - r-tidyr >=0.8.2
    - r-writexl >=0.2
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dt >=0.9
    - r-mass
    - r-base64enc
    - r-broom >=0.5.2
    - r-bslib >=0.3.1
    - r-car >=3.0_0
    - r-curl >=2.5
    - r-dplyr >=1.0.7
    - r-ggplot2 >=2.2.1
    - r-glue >=1.3.0
    - r-import >=1.1.0
    - r-jsonlite >=1.0
    - r-knitr >=1.20
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.4
    - r-magrittr >=1.5
    - r-markdown >=1.0
    - r-patchwork >=1.0.0
    - r-plotly >=4.7.1
    - r-png
    - r-psych >=1.8.4
    - r-randomizr >=0.20.0
    - r-readr >=1.1.1
    - r-readxl >=1.0.0
    - r-rlang >=0.4.10
    - r-rmarkdown >=1.14
    - r-rstudioapi >=0.7
    - r-scales >=0.4.0
    - r-shiny >=1.7.1
    - r-shinyace >=0.4.1
    - r-shinyfiles >=0.9.1
    - r-stringi >=1.2.4
    - r-tibble >=1.4.2
    - r-tidyr >=0.8.2
    - r-writexl >=0.2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('radiant.data')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('radiant.data')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/radiant-rstats/radiant.data, https://radiant-rstats.github.io/radiant.data, https://radiant-rstats.github.io/docs
  license: AGPL-3.0-only
  summary: The Radiant Data menu includes interfaces for loading, saving, viewing, visualizing, summarizing, transforming, and combining data. It also contains functionality to generate reproducible reports of the analyses conducted in the application.
  license_family: AGPL
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/AGPL-3
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
